{
  "stem": "13469.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 2.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But anyway, they built-- of course, as we found out later on-- big fortifications and guns and placements and all that sort of thing by Zandvoort and all the way there, along the beach.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they presumably thought that Jews were not wanted in that area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I mean, I'm surprised they didn't let anybody live in that area.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But, but it wasn't-- everybody else was all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "But Jews were not allowed to live in that area.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we had to move.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "This was before.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Later on, all Jews had to move to Amsterdam.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then we were well aware of that.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we were caught by that as well.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But this was very early in September.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So only six months after the invasion, really, we had to move from Heemstede, where we'd lived for four years very happily.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "We had to move away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we moved to a place called Naarden, which is just east of Amsterdam, near Hilversum, which is better known, because that's the radio station.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "So we went live in Naarden, in [DUTCH], number 31.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Naarden is, in Dutch, a [DUTCH], I never really worked out, exactly, what the English word for that is-- like a fortress, a medieval fortress town with a moat all the way around it and, and a wall around it for, for defending the town.",
      "word_count": 45
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that's what it was.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And on the inside, there were loads of houses and a school and a church and all that sort of thing.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And we went to school inside this fortress area in the middle of Naarden.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "So we went to, to yet another school-- same language, fortunately.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And we stayed there for, I think, the best part of a year, in Naarden.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
